I"><h2 id="step-1-install-etcher">Step 1: Install Etcher</h2>
<p>Etcher is the tool which we recommend you use to install the operating systems.
If you want to you can also use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dd</code> or any other tool.</p>

<p>For most Operating Systems you can go <a href="https://www.balena.io/etcher/">here</a> to the official link to download it.</p>

